## ğŸ¯ Design Tokens

### Colors
- **Primary**: #00484F (dark teal)
- **Accent**: #FBEA1B (yellow)
- **Neutrals**: 50-900 scale
- **Semantic**: success, warning, danger, info

### Typography
- **Font Family**: Public Sans
- **Scale**: xs (12px) to 4xl (46px)
- **Weights**: normal (400), medium (500), semibold (600), bold (700)

### Spacing
8px-based system: xs (8px), sm (16px), md (24px), lg (32px), xl (48px), 2xl (64px)

### Border Radius
sm (4px), md (6px), lg (8px), xl (10px), 2xl (32px), full (9999px - pill)

